(X,d)
 \beta(\mu,\nu) = \sup \left( \left|\int_X f\ d(\mu-\nu)\right| : f\in {\rm Lip}(X),\  \sup_{x\in X}|f(x)|\leq 1 \right),
{\rm Lip}(X):=\left( f:X\to{\mathbb R}, |f(x)-f(y)|\leq d(x,y) {\rm \ for\ all\ } x,y\in X   \right). 
